      <hedline>
        <hl1>Back of the Envelope</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Fund-raising by private equity is continuing at rapid pace; Thomson Financial reports that 35 funds have raised total of $36.2 billion in first quarter, up 39 percent from first quarter of 2006; graph (M)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Fund-raising by private equity is continuing at a torrid pace. In the first quarter, 35 funds raised a total of $36.2 billion, according to Thomson Financial. While the dollar amount is down from the record fourth quarter of last year, it is up 39 percent from the first quarter of 2006.</p>
      </block>
